data.description: Don't miss this EXCEPTIONAL LOCATION - peaceful COUNTRYSIDE LIVING with all the CITY CONVENIENCE plus EASY ACCESS to Peterson SFB, Schreiver SFB and The Mountain Post – Fort Carson! You will love this SPACIOUS FLOOR PLAN with OFFICE / FLEX space on the Main and LARGE LOFT on the Upper.  The BEAUTIFUL KITCHEN is BIG/OPEN and has GENEROUS CABINET SPACE and GRANITE COUNTERS plus pantry, island, and stainless steel appliances. HUGE PRIMARY RETREAT includes 5-piece bath & walk-in closet. Convenient UPSTAIRS LAUNDRY near the bedrooms and FRESH PAINT THROUGHOUT!   Newer water softener and BRAND NEW WATER HEATER in May ’23, plus Humidifier with Lennox PureAir PCO20-28 Air Purifier, whole house MERV-16 AIR FILTRATION SYSTEM and prewired for your Security System.   You'll be comfortable year round with A/C in addition to ceiling fans in every bedroom, the living room and loft.  Spread out with tons of storage in the INSULATED AND DRYWALLED GARAGE plus the large under-stairs closet and big shed out back. And you can relax in peace with an amazing MOUNTAIN BACKDROP on the welcoming FRONT PORCH or FENCED BACKYARD.    Located in Terrific El Paso County Location, So No City Taxes! Water Provider is Colorado Centre Metropolitan District (Not the City of Fountain). Close proximity to Abundant Green Space w/WALKING TRAILS & MULTIPLE PARKS w/Rock Climbing, Basketball, Skating & New "Centre Barkway" Dog Park. Myriad of Shopping & Dining Destinations w/Quick Access to Bradley Rd & Powers/Mesa Ridge Pkwy. 15 Minutes or Less To Peterson SFB, Shreiver SFB and Fort Carson.  Don’t miss the 3D walkthrough virtual tour!
